;; check:test-tags allowlist — libs whose deftests are not yet backfilled with a
;; pyramid tag (^:unit / ^:integration / ^:contract). BOU-166 enforces exactly
;; one pyramid tag per deftest; these repo-relative path prefixes are exempt
;; until their lib is backfilled. Remove a prefix once its lib is tagged.
;;
;; Enforced now (not exempt): user, admin, platform, core, realtime, tenant,
;; observability, e2e, tools, jobs, cache, storage, and every already-fully-tagged
;; lib (workflow, search, push, payments, i18n, geo, external, email, calendar,
;; boundary-mcp).
{:allow-untagged
 ["libs/boundary-cli/"
  "libs/devtools/"
  "libs/scaffolder/"
  "libs/reports/"
  "libs/ui-style/"
  "libs/audience/"
  "libs/ai/"
  "test/"]}
